{"tid":535502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係你呀陳生?] 山頂到灣仔索價500 外籍女不從遭的士司機毆打兼劫200元","createTime":"2018-01-21T03:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T15:19:30.000Z","uid":42820,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f5670702de8cd1584c2254d9ef0ca78a0da4fc","tid":535502,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:00:28.000Z","msg":"山頂到灣仔索價500　外籍女不從遭的士司機毆打兼劫200元<br />\n<br />\n一名26歲外籍女子凌晨2時許在山頂截乘的士，前往灣仔皇后大道東200號囍滙對開，抵達目的地後，司機索價500元車資，女事主拒絕，雙方爭執，司機繼而將她載至一個不明地方，揮拳打傷其左眼，再從其銀包取去約200元港幣，駕車折返囍滙對開放下女事主，揚長而去。<br />\n<br />\n女事主返回囍滙寓所報警，清醒由救護車送院治理，警方接報到場，列作「行劫」處理，交由灣仔警區刑事調查第3隊跟進，正追查一名年齡30歲至40歲男子下落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180121/s00001/1516494916139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180121%2Fs00001%2F1516494916139&d=irIEEVvA7ca%2BemMB6FcfEUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=640672f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180121%2Fs00001%2F1516494916139&h=8df1efd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180121/s00001/1516494916139</a>"},{"pid":"5008f61895c02378c0f13204579ced06a13085f3","tid":535502,"uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"03e243dcf5fb67df053e93f86915bd0680815a2f","tid":535502,"uid":6717,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"5008f61895c02378c0f13204579ced06a13085f3","tid":535502,"uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"睇清楚d內容啦 關metoo咩事 係又抽唔係又抽"},{"pid":"9755e71f1580f61ac4e7b2d7b4a3274173c83beb","tid":535502,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:19:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21a3482f0f376de